      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;dhcp-troubleshooting&#34;&gt;DHCP Troubleshooting&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#get-an-api-token&#34;&gt;Get an API token&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#1-confirm-the-status-of-the-cray-dhcp-kea-services&#34;&gt;1 Confirm the status of the &lt;code&gt;cray-dhcp-kea&lt;/code&gt; services&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#11-check-cray-dchp-kea-pods&#34;&gt;Check &lt;code&gt;cray-dchp-kea&lt;/code&gt; pods&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#12-check-cray-dhcp-kea-service-endpoints&#34;&gt;Check &lt;code&gt;cray-dhcp-kea&lt;/code&gt; service endpoints&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#13-verify-that-cray-dhcp-kea-configuration-is-valid&#34;&gt;Verify that &lt;code&gt;cray-dhcp-kea&lt;/code&gt; configuration is valid&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#14-review-cray-dhcp-kea-running-configuration&#34;&gt;Review &lt;code&gt;cray-dhcp-kea&lt;/code&gt; running configuration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#15-verify-that-cray-dhcp-kea-has-active-dhcp-leases&#34;&gt;Verify that &lt;code&gt;cray-dhcp-kea&lt;/code&gt; has active DHCP leases&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#16-check-dhcp-helperpy-output&#34;&gt;Check &lt;code&gt;dhcp-helper.py&lt;/code&gt; output&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-13/troubleshooting/dhcp_runbook/#17-check-cray-dhcp-kea-logs&#34;&gt;Check &lt;code&gt;cray-dhcp-kea&lt;/code&gt; logs&lt;/a&gt;&l